{"tid":937363,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好灰 好想死 唔想讀書 唔想做人","createTime":"2018-12-11T13:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T10:59:36.000Z","uid":195975,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0bbc5f1288b4d273af3e016b553c9bb274ce526e","tid":937363,"uid":195975,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:13:49.000Z","msg":"點解自己會連朋友都識唔到<br />\n明明自己都努力搭話<br />\n明明自己都有誠意<br />\n好想死<br />\n自己好冇用<br />\n明明好簡單<br />\n明明正常人都得<br />\n點解我唔得<br />\n點解我冇社交生活<br />\n點解我聖誕都係自己一個<br />\n好冇用啊自己<br />\n點解要將自己變成孤島<br />\n點解要咁驚人<br />\n點解成日逃避社交<br />\n點解我地約我都搵籍口出街<br />\n點解自己去到眾會都摺埋一邊<br />\n點解我咁怪<br />\n點解其他人咁易識朋友<br />\n好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4481ef04aef09e121972ca023a9bf26705469dc0","tid":937363,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17985c78e108f8cced755cccb0b4ffbe09057401","tid":937363,"uid":198998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:15:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29a9cb064d358691e3967ef3db5b7b4aa48a198","tid":937363,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:15:57.000Z","msg":"去旅行見識下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  困死係香港梗係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0514334dc4943009a93182efa32ff2f8ca0c4e","tid":937363,"uid":82450,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:19:22.000Z","msg":"On撚尻<br />\n聖誕出街個d先叫唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712754993bd62f57029ad343a36566fe9dbdccf9","tid":937363,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b29a9cb064d3